        <p class="reveal">The audience of Michaela Cibulková mainly comprises young women (age 15-30) and young couples (age 25-40), owners of at least one dog. I interviewed six people from the target group, and they found some common ground:</p>

        <ul>
            <li class="reveal">It is important to know the photographer - know them, feel close to them, see a lot of their work before making a decision</li>
            <li class="reveal">The demand for photography varies throughout the year; most of them prefer their photos to be taken during fall, spring, or in the snow, and they enjoy discounted and special shooting offers during these times.</li>
